article.description: — Juan Felix Rodriguez had 16 points and six rebounds as Stony Brook topped NJIT 56-44 on Sunday.
article.headline: Rodriguez scores 16 to lift Stony Brook past NJIT 56-44
article.linkText: Rodriguez scores 16 to lift Stony Brook past NJIT 56-44
article.story: NEWARK, N.J. -- — Juan Felix Rodriguez had 16 points and six rebounds as Stony Brook topped NJIT 56-44 on Sunday. Frankie Policelli had 11 points for Stony Brook (7-7, 5-3 America East Conference). Mouhamadou Gueye added 14 rebounds. Both teams set season lows for scoring in the first half when Stony Brook took a 21-13 lead. Dylan O’Hearn had 12 points for the Highlanders (5-7, 4-6). NJIT defeated Stony Brook 74-65 on Saturday.
